definition.value: An indoledione that is 1H-indole-5,6-dione substituted by a carboxy group at position 2.
A 2-hydroxydicarboxylic acid that is malic acid carrying an additional phosphinomethyl substituent at position 2.
A hydroxyisoflavone that is isoflavone substituted by hydroxy groups at positions 5, 7 and 3' and methoxy groups at positions 6, 4' and 5' respectively.
An amino cyclitol glycoside that is isolated from Streptomyces kasugaensis and exhibits antibiotic and fungicidal properties.
